OL,3,CMental health app created by suicide
OL,4,Csurvivor sees rocketing demand
OL,6,FAn app which was developed by a man
OL,7,Fwho tried to take his own life has
OL,8,Fbeen revamped due to rocketing demand
OL,9,Ffor mental health help.
OL,11,FThe app was the brain-child of former
OL,12,Fcomedian Jake Mills who originated the
OL,13,F"Hub of Hope" following his own battle
OL,14,Fwith depression and attempted suicide
OL,15,Fin 2013.
