OL,3,CMental health app created by suicide
OL,4,Csurvivor sees rocketing demand
OL,6,FHe heads the charity Chasing the
OL,7,FStigma, which he founded to help
OL,8,Fothers in a similar situation, having
OL,9,Fgone public on social, and other,
OL,10,Fmedia about his own mental health
OL,11,Fissues during his recovery.
OL,13,FThe app has now been overhauled to
OL,14,Fmake it more effective after there was
OL,15,Fa 66 percent increase in demand for
OL,16,Fhelp since 2023, with an average of
OL,17,F25,700 visitors per month searching
OL,18,Ffor help last year alone.
