OL,6,FJake Mills, from Liverpool, said:
OL,7,F"When I first spoke out about my
OL,8,Fmental health issues in 2014, people
OL,9,Fwere already waiting far too long to
OL,10,Faccess help on the NHS, and too many
OL,11,Fwere slipping through the cracks
OL,12,Fbecause they didn't know where to turn
OL,13,Fto for help.
