OL,4,Csurvivor sees rocketing demand
OL,6,FThe app directs users to national
OL,7,Fcharities like MIND which offer help
OL,8,Fto people needing support with their
OL,9,Fmental health, starting from a small
OL,10,Fspreadsheet developed by Jake at his
OL,11,Fmum's dining table.
OL,13,FThe free app now has more than 14,500
OL,14,Fservices across the UK listed and it
OL,15,Fhas been used by more than 800,000
OL,16,Fpeople since 2017.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G5/7
