OL,4,Csurvivor sees rocketing demand
OL,6,FJake adds, "After being included,
OL,7,Fwithout warning, in the 2021 pandemic
OL,8,Fshielding letter and, more recently,
OL,9,Fin government's national suicide
OL,10,Fprevention strategy, we saw a steep
OL,11,Fincrease in visitors to the Hub.
OL,13,F"This not only showed how desperately
OL,14,Fneeded this resource is, but it also
OL,15,Fmade strengthening the Hub's
OL,16,Finfrastructure absolutely critical if
OL,17,Fwe were to continue to provide clear
OL,18,Fpathways to help."
