OL,3,CMental health app created by suicide
OL,4,Csurvivor sees rocketing demand
OL,6,F"Our app really has never been more
OL,7,Fvital. We want more people to be able
OL,8,Fto get help for their mental health
OL,9,Fissues before they reach crisis point.
OL,11,F"The relaunch of the Hub of Hope marks
OL,12,Fa new chapter in our mission to
OL,13,Fdestigmatise mental health and our
OL,14,Fteam has worked tirelessly to ensure
OL,15,Fthat the new design is accessible for
OL,16,Fall."
